PrecisEnactment of a WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER (LITTLE SALMON/CARMACKS FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of certain land in the Yukon in order to facilitate the settlement of Aboriginal land claims, and (b) the repeal of an earlier Withdrawal Order (P.C. 1996-1869).

precis:
Enactment of a WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER (LITTLE SALMON/CARMACKS FIRST
NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of
certain land in the Yukon in order to facilitate the settlement of
Aboriginal land claims, and (b) the repeal of an earlier Withdrawal Order
(P.C. 1996-1869).
